					<div class="counter-section">

						<h5 class="section-title">Overview</h5>

						<p>As part of Faculty process filling the details of faculty in the AYUSH Education Portal. This service enables to faculty to fill the form of all the faculty details after <b>Sign In</b> to the portal. Faculty will receive an Email from Ayush Education Portal .</p>

						<h5 class="section-title">Step-by-Step Guide</h5>
						<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 1: </span>Faculty will be redirected to Dashboard after login where Faculty can select options available in Menu as per need.
						</p>

						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="assets/img/module_guide_img/nch/faculty/nch-faculty-3.png"
								alt="nch-faculty-1" title="nch-faculty-1"
								class="img-fluid">
						</div>


						<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 2: </span> Faculty has to fill it's details for which select <span class="text-heighlight">FACULTY DETAILS  >  FACULTY FORM > Faculty Details</span> from menu.
							The <b>Faculty details</b> would have been uploaded by the <b>Institute</b>, and  their basic parameters will  be pre-filled.
							
						</p>

						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="assets/img/module_guide_img/nch/faculty/nch-faculty-4.png"
								alt="nch-faculty-2" title="nch-faculty-2"
								class="img-fluid">
						</div>


						<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 3: </span>To save the details for the next process, it is necessary to fill in all the details in the <b>Personal Details</b> tab and then click on the <b>Save as Draft</b> button.
You can navigate to the next step tab by using the <b>Next</b> button provided below.
						</p>



						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="assets/img/module_guide_img/nch/faculty/nch-faculty-5.png"
								alt="nch-faculty-3" title="nch-faculty-3"
								class="img-fluid">
						</div>
						
						<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 4: </span>Same as a above step of <b>Personal Details</b> user need to fill up the process form that are visible in tab format like "Qualification", "Registration Details" etc. after click on the <b>Save as Draft</b> button.
You can navigate to the next step tab by using the <b>Next</b> button provided below.
						</p>
						
							<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 5: </span>The ultimate step in the process is the <b>Confirmation tab</b>, which can be denoted as the  <b>Final step</b>. It is mandatory to read the <b>Declaration</b> and select the checkbox before clicking the <b>Final submit</b> button, which will submit all the saved draft details from the preceding stages. Please be aware that no modifications or revisions can be made to the details after the <b>Final submission</b>, as per the instructions provided. Hence, it is crucial to thoroughly review and verify all the details before proceeding to click the Final submit button.
							Once you complete the <b>Final submission</b>, a notification will be displayed, indicating that your final <b>Faculty Details</b> have been forwarded to the higher authority for <b>approval</b>.
						</p>



						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="assets/img/module_guide_img/nch/faculty/nch-faculty-6.png"
								alt="nch-faculty-4" title="nch-faculty-4"
								class="img-fluid">
						</div>
						
						<p class="custom-step">
							<span class="custom-step-title">STEP 6: </span>Upon clicking the <b>View Faculty Details</b> button, all filled details can be accessed. Once approved by higher authority, the <b>Teacher Code</b> will become visible.
						</p>



						<div class="custom-stepimg">
							<img
								src="assets/img/module_guide_img/nch/faculty/nch-faculty-7.png"
								alt="nch-faculty-5" title="nch-faculty-5"
								class="img-fluid">
						</div>
						
					</div>

